_sText: My very first Source map complete with master light switch, gas chamber, hidden anti-gravity switch, and Nightvision for everyone for when the lights go out (all players spawn on top of NVGs). A bit too big and open for gg but hey, not bad for my first Source map, not to mention the scripting involved in making the NVG entity (you wont find NVGs on ANY other map unless you buy them).
